  "prompt": "Does the new start up stay uncle allow admission to unmarried couples in delhi?",
  "response": "As of my knowledge cutoff in October 2023, **StayUncle** is a startup that offers accommodation solutions, typically focusing on providing homestays and shared living spaces. Policies regarding the acceptance of unmarried couples can vary based on the specific regulations of the platform, the individual hosts, and local laws in Delhi.\n\nHere are some steps you can take to determine whether StayUncle allows admission for unmarried couples in Delhi:\n\n1. **Check the Official Website or App:**\n   - Visit StayUncle's official website or download their app to review their terms and policies. They may have specific guidelines regarding bookings for unmarried couples.\n\n2. **Contact Customer Support:**\n   - Reach out directly to StayUncle's customer service or support team. They can provide the most accurate and up-to-date information regarding their policies.\n\n3. **Review Host Policies:**\n   - If StayUncle operates on a platform model where individual hosts list their properties, each host may have their own set of rules. Make sure to read the listing details carefully or communicate directly with the host to confirm their stance on unmarried couples.\n\n4. **Local Regulations:**\n   - While Delhi is generally progressive, some landlords or hosts may have personal preferences or restrictions based on societal norms. It's always best to discuss and confirm any concerns beforehand.\n\n5. **Look for Verified Accommodations:**\n   - Some platforms offer verified listings that adhere to certain standards and policies. Choosing such accommodations might reduce the likelihood of facing restrictions.\n\n**Recommendation:**\nTo ensure a smooth booking experience, it's advisable to communicate openly with StayUncle and potential hosts about your situation. This proactive approach can help avoid any misunderstandings and ensure that both parties are comfortable with the arrangement.\n\nIf you encounter any difficulties or need further assistance, consider reaching out to customer reviews or forums where other users might have shared their experiences regarding similar situations with StayUncle in Delhi.",
